&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bow &amp;amp; Arrow is a fairly simple game. As I remember 2017, it was the dawn of VR games. Not that weren&amp;rsquo;t made before, but mechanics and dynamics still haven&amp;rsquo;t been fully explored. Many VR arcades looked for a cutting edge, propietry games that players could play only in that specific arcade. Bow &amp;amp; Arrow was one of those games.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
